{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "At first I prayed for light:"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Could I but see the way,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "How gladly, swiftly would I walk"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "To everlasting day!"
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "And next I prayed for strength:"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "That I might tread the road"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "With firm, unfaltering feet, and win"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "The heaven’s serene abode."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "And then I asked for faith:"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Could I but trust my God,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "I’d live infolded in His peace,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Though foes were all abroad."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "But now I pray for love:"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Deep love to God and man;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "A living love that will not fail,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "However dark His plan."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "And light and strength and faith"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Are opening everywhere!"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "God waited patiently until"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "I prayed the larger prayer."
        }
      ],
      "number": 5
    }
  ],
  "title": "At First I Prayed for Light"
}
